attributionInfo.brokerName: Arizona Metropolitan Realty & Management CO. LLC

data.description: Home, sweet home! Located in the desirable Gladden Farms, this charming single-level residence epitomizes comfort and convenience. Nestled on a corner lot providing 3 beds, 2 baths, a 3-car garage, and a mature landscape. Enter to find inviting living spaces paired with abundant natural light, tall ceilings, and tasteful flooring - carpet & tile throughout. Entertainment-ready, this gem offers pre-wired surround sound! The kitchen boasts built-in appliances, a walk-in pantry, and ample cabinetry & counter space. Primary bedroom has a full bathroom for added ease. Outside, the perfectly sized backyard awaits! Featuring a covered patio to relax, a home garden, and a fenced area ideal for a dog run. Don't miss out on this gem!
